    <id>tag:dexpairs.xyz,2021-08-07:protocols-full-support-aave-v2</id>
    <!--<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://dexpairs.xyz/news?title=protocols-support-aave-v2"/>-->
    <title>Full support of Aave v2 protocol</title>
    <published>2021-08-07T21:00:00Z</published>
    <updated>2021-08-07T21:00:00Z</updated>
    <content type="xhtml">
      <div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
        <h2 class="chapter-title">Track your Aave tokens on Ethereum and Polygon</h2>
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            Aave v2 tokens are fully supported on Ethereum and Polygon !<br />
            Track your collateral tokens, monitor your borrowed assets, and your debt is taken into account in the global wallet value.
          </p>
        </div>
        <h2 class="chapter-title">Partial support of Compound and Venus</h2>
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            Compound (Ethereum) and Venus (Binance Smart Chain) are partially supported.<br />
            Only collateral tokens have a value, the borrowed tokens don't have price yet.
          </p>
        </div>
